title.rendered: Sorrento All Weather Aluminium Bar Stool – end of line

content.rendered:
*This item is end of line and available whilst stocks last* (This item was £137ea)

The Sorrento Bar Stool is made from a gorgeous aluminium frame frame with a faux vintage distressed finish. It comes in a choice of 4 colours and also has tables specifically designed to work as a set. Finished with a clear lacquer to deter further chipping. Each stool is individually distressed for a unique look! Ideal for indoor or outdoor use!

In stock for delivery in 3-5 working days.

CTAS tested and comes with a 12 month guarantee.

For use indoors and outdoors.
